{"text_id":177547,"tokens":["This"," paper"," presents"," a"," novel"," approach"," to"," relation"," detection"," for"," KB","QA"," by"," introducing"," a"," hierarchical"," recurrent"," neural"," network"," enhanced"," by"," residual"," learning","."," The"," proposed"," method"," uses"," deep"," residual"," bidirectional"," LST","Ms"," to"," compare"," questions"," and"," relation"," names"," at"," different"," levels"," of"," abstraction","."," Additionally",","," a"," KB","QA"," system"," is"," proposed"," that"," integrates"," entity"," linking"," and"," the"," relation"," detector","."," The"," experimental"," results"," demonstrate"," that"," the"," proposed"," approach"," not"," only"," achieves"," outstanding"," relation"," detection"," performance",","," but"," also"," helps"," the"," KB","QA"," system"," achieve"," state","-","of","-","the","-","art"," accuracy"," for"," both"," single","-","relation"," and"," multi","-","relation"," QA"," benchmarks",".","\n","The"," paper"," is"," well","-","written"," and"," organized",","," and"," the"," ideas"," are"," clearly"," presented","."," The"," proposed"," approach"," is"," novel"," and"," the"," experimental"," results"," demonstrate"," its"," effectiveness","."," The"," authors"," should"," be"," commended"," for"," their"," contributions"," to"," the"," field"," of"," KB","QA",".","\n","The"," authors"," could"," further"," improve"," the"," paper"," by"," providing"," more"," detail"," about"," the"," implementation"," of"," the"," proposed"," approach","."," Additionally",","," more"," discussion"," of"," the"," results"," and"," how"," they"," compare"," to"," existing"," methods"," would"," be"," beneficial","."," Finally",","," the"," authors"," should"," consider"," expanding"," the"," experimental"," evaluation"," to"," include"," more"," datasets"," and"," tasks","."],"sub_source":"peerread","model":"davinci","label":1}